; OpenADS ACE-compatible DLL exports.
; All entry points use the Microsoft __cdecl convention (the SAP ACE
; default on Windows). Names are exported undecorated on x64 and x86;
; __cdecl on x86 prepends a leading underscore at link time, but the
; .def NAME form forces the public export to match the source name.
LIBRARY
EXPORTS
    AdsConnect60
    AdsDisconnect
    AdsOpenTable
    AdsCloseTable
    AdsGotoTop
    AdsGotoBottom
    AdsSkip
    AdsAtEOF
    AdsAtBOF
    AdsGetField
    AdsGetFieldName
    AdsGetNumFields
    AdsGetFieldType
    AdsGetFieldLength
    AdsGetRecordNum
    AdsGetRecordCount
    AdsGetLastError
    AdsGetVersion
    AdsAppendRecord
    AdsWriteRecord
    AdsDeleteRecord
    AdsRecallRecord
    AdsIsRecordDeleted
    AdsSetString
    AdsSetLogical
    AdsSetDouble
    AdsLockRecord
    AdsUnlockRecord
    AdsLockTable
    AdsUnlockTable
    AdsFlushFileBuffers
    AdsOpenIndex
    AdsCloseIndex
    AdsCloseAllIndexes
    AdsCreateIndex
    AdsDeleteIndex
    AdsGetNumIndexes
    AdsGetIndexHandle
    AdsGetIndexHandleByOrder
    AdsGetIndexExpr
    AdsGetIndexName
    AdsSetIndexDirection
    AdsSeek
    AdsSeekLast
    AdsSetScope
    AdsClearScope
    AdsGetScope
    AdsPackTable
    AdsZapTable
    AdsSetAOF
    AdsGetAOFOptLevel
    AdsClearAOF
    AdsGetMemoLength
    AdsGetMemoDataType
    AdsBinaryToFile
    AdsFileToBinary
    AdsGetLastAutoinc
    AdsEnableEncryption
    AdsDisableEncryption
    AdsIsEncryptionEnabled
    AdsIsTableEncrypted
    AdsIsRecordEncrypted
    AdsEncryptTable
    AdsDecryptTable
    AdsEncryptRecord
    AdsDecryptRecord
    AdsBeginTransaction
    AdsCommitTransaction
    AdsRollbackTransaction
    AdsInTransaction
    AdsCreateSavepoint
    AdsRollbackTransaction80
    AdsDDCreate
    AdsDDAddTable
    AdsDDRemoveTable
    AdsCreateSQLStatement
    AdsCloseSQLStatement
    AdsPrepareSQL
    AdsExecuteSQL
    AdsExecuteSQLDirect
